thread.title: BRIEF-Guangdong Anjubao Digital Technology sees FY 2017 net profit down 43.18 pct to 71.59 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Guangdong Anjubao Digital Technology sees FY 2017 net profit down 43.18 pct to 71.59 pct

organizations.name: guangdong anjubao digital technology co ltd

text:
Jan 31(Reuters) - Guangdong Anjubao Digital Technology Co Ltd
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to decrease by 43.18 percent to 71.59 percent, or to be 5 million yuan to 10 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 17.6 million yuan
* Says increased costs is the main reason for the forecast
